                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>36.32 mm (1.430 in)</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Pot flywheel minimum thickness after resurfacing</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>39.37 mm (1.550 in)</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="2" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>Requires measurement from crankshaft mounting surface of flywheel to clutch
                                    surface of flywheel.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
